text: Bumetopia fornicatoides is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1980. It is known from the Philippines.BioLib.cz - Bumetopia fornicatoides. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Homonoeini Category:Beetles described in 1980
